-

-less   bez- prefix

*

* absence, non existence   ni- prefix

* across   prě- prefix

* again   prě- prefix

* any-   ně- prefix

* because, in order to ...   -radma suffix

* comparative (better)   lučše article

* comparative (worst sense)   1 liše article 2 liše adv.

* down   niz- prefix

* enforces meaning   prě- prefix

* expression of opposites   ot- prefix

* identity expression   -žde suffix

* makes querying verb   li article

* makes relative pronoun or adverb   -že suffix

* more (comparative)   više article

* multiplication, -ple   -krat suffix

* negation   ne- prefix

* over-   prě- prefix

* perfective verb for-, through-   pro- prefix

* perfective verb with sense with-, at-, in-   pri- prefix

* perform an action over something (perfective verb)   1 o- prefix 2 po- prefix

* prefix with, together   s(o)- prefix

* re-   prě- prefix

* some-   ně- prefix

* start an action (perfective verb)   vaz- prefix

* the best (positive superlative)   najlučše article

* the most (superlative)   1 naj- prefix 2 najviše article

* the worst (negative superlative)   najliše article

* to finish some process (makes perfective verb)   iz- prefix

* to perform an action (perfective verb)   na- prefix
